org.apache.drill

Class SingleRowListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.SingleRowListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UserResultsListener

    public abstract class SingleRowListener
extends Object
implements UserResultsListener
    Result listener that is set up to receive a single row. Useful for queries such with a count(*) or limit 1. The abstract method rowArrived(QueryDataBatch) provides the means for a derived class to get the expected record's data.
